title: 2016 Week 13 review
itunes:title: 2016 Week 13 review
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, and Gregg Rosenthal – go game-by-game breaking down all the Week 13 action which included the Chiefs shocking the Falcons with some late-game heroics in Atlanta, and a big come-back win for the Raiders to move to the top of the AFC.
